                                                        @Html.DropDownListFor(Model => Model.tag.Flag, new SelectList(ViewBag.Trangthai, "id", "flag"), new { @id = "tagidadd_flag", @class = "form-control flagtagidadd", required = "required" })
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>


                                        <div class="modal-footer">

                                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Đóng</button>
                                            <button type="button" id="btnthemtagid" class="btn btn-success waves-effect waves-light m-r-30">Thêm</button>

                                        </div>
                                    </form>


                                </div>

                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div id="suatagid" class="modal fade" role="dialog">
                            <div class="modal-dialog  modal-lg">

                                <!-- Modal content-->
                                <div class="modal-content">
                                    <div class="modal-header">
                                        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>
                                        <h4 class="modal-title">Sửa tag id</h4>
                                    </div>

                                    <form data-toggle="validator" class="form-horizontal">
                                        <div class="modal-body">
                                            <div class="white-box m-b-0">
                                                <h3 class="box-title m-b-0">Thông tin tag id</h3>
                                                <div class="form-group">
                                                    <label class="col-md-12"> Tag ID </label>
                                                    <div class="col-md-12">
                                                        @Html.TextBoxFor(model => model.tag.TagID, "", new { @type = "text", @class = "form-control matagtagidedit", @placeholder = "Mã tag", @required = "required", @readonly = "readonly" })
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="form-group">
                                                    <label class="col-md-12"> Tên tag </label>
                                                    <div class="col-md-12">
                                                        @Html.TextBoxFor(model => model.tag.TenTag, "", new { @type = "text", @class = "form-control tentagtagidedit", @placeholder = "Mã loại", @required = "required" })
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="form-group">
                                                    <label class="col-md-12"> Mã chức vụ </label>
                                                    <div class="col-md-12">
                                                        @Html.DropDownListFor(Model => Model.tag.Machucvu, new SelectList(Model.listchucvu, "machucvu", "tenchucvu"), new { @id = "tagidedit_chucvu", @class = "form-control chucvutagidedit", required = "required" })
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>


                                        <div class="modal-footer">

                                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Đóng</button>
                                            <button type="button" id="btnsuatagid" class="btn btn-success waves-effect waves-light m-r-30">Lưu</button>

                                        </div>
                                    </form>


                                </div>

                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Thanh ẩn -->
                        <div class="panel">
                            Ẩn cột:  <a class="toggle-vis" id="ttagid" data-column="1"> Tên tag </a> / <a class="toggle-vis" id="ttagid" data-column="2">Mã chức vụ</a> / <a class="toggle-vis" id="ttagid" data-column="3">Flag</a> / <a class="toggle-vis" id="ttagid" data-column="4">Chức năng</a>
                        </div>
                        <!-- table -->
                        <div class="table-responsive">
                            <table id="tagidTable" class="table table-striped">
                                <thead>
                                    <tr>
                                        <th>Tag id</th>
                                        <th>Tên tag</th>
                                        <th>Mã chức vụ</th>
                                        <th>Flag</th>
                                        <th>Chức năng</th>
                                    </tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody>
                                    @foreach (var item in Model.listag)
                                    {
                                        <tr>
                                            <td class="matagid">@item.TagID</td>
                                            <td>@item.TenTag</td>
                                            <td>@item.Machucvu</td>
                                            <td>
                                                <a class="btnloaibaidangflag" data-matagid="@item.TagID" hres="#">
                                                    @if (@item.Flag == true)
                                                    {
                                                        <span class="text-info"> Không khóa </span>
                                                    }
                                                    else
                                                    {
                                                        <span class="text-danger"> Khóa </span>
                                                    }
                                                </a>
                                            </td>
                                            <td>
                                                <button class="btnloadtagid" type="button" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#suatagid" style="background-color:transparent;border:none">
                                                    <i class="fa fa-pencil-square-o" style="color:red"> </i>
                                                </button>
                                                @*<button type="button" style="background-color:transparent;border:none">
                                    <i class="fa fa-info" style="color:blue"> </i>
                                </button>*@
                                            </td>

                                        </tr>
                                    }


                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                    </div>
